{"tid":739251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名女子從馬來西亞回港後確診霍亂 現時情況穩定","createTime":"2018-07-12T03:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T14:58:18.000Z","uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a42a6abcf52ef835795c7a162e73583b47769b08","tid":739251,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"一名女子從馬來西亞回港後，確診霍亂，衞生防護中心列為外地傳入個案，現時在瑪嘉烈醫院接受隔離治療，情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n這名25歲女子在上月30日至上星期二期間，到過馬來西亞，上星期二開始出現腹瀉、腹痛、噁心及嘔吐，星期日入院，並於昨日出院，她的糞便樣本經化驗後，證實含產生腸毒素的霍亂弧菌O1小川型。<br />\n<br />\n初步調查顯示，病人最近外遊時並沒有同行人士，她的家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵，衞生防護中心正繼續調查個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406495-20180711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406495-20180711.htm&d=3l4Hg6ZQgzo2poxeTVxz%2B%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ffdc439d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406495-20180711.htm&h=1775a00d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406495-20180711.htm</a>"},{"pid":"33195b1f75be89d506b64ddc9fbc590a58cb15d8","tid":739251,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69788319d4ebcf20f57f17d107d2e6020253e42","tid":739251,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"70%支那狗"},{"pid":"30ebbc422542d2f773d4b7b3a6072cb97a97ad85","tid":739251,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"幾耐冇聽過霍亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起以前政府有個宣傳廣告<br />\n小販檔涼粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />